name: Ancient Tablets of King Femi: Emerald
description:
Placed deep in the Southern jungle.
Humidity etched into the message.
The tablet that breathes.
The tablet that is alive.
Sits beneath the damp earth and soil.
Cruelest of creatures dare not walk in its path.
Yet the flowers above grow in its colour and bloom in light of it's love.
Truth.
Realisation.
Written into the fibres of the earth.
